title: Boyz II Trend 10/2: QANON Measure, Mike Lee, 4 - 10

description:
On this edition of Boyz II Trend Miles and DJ Danl discuss a measure condemning QANON passed 371-18, Mike Lee tests positive for COVID-19, and people are discussing their four favorite 10/10 games of the last generation (Miles and DJ Danl do not adhere to generational restrictions).
